Name: TypeOfResult
Description: Identifies the specific type of result. Supports the use of an external controlled vocabulary.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the Results Detail. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: ResultsDate
Description: The date or date range of obtaining results from the development work.

Name: RequirementsAssessment
Description: Description of whether specific requirements for the activities providing these results were met.
